Italy's consumer price index rose 0.4 pctin March compared with February after an identical increase inFebruary over January, the national statistics institute Istatsaid.    The year-on-year rise in March was 4.2 pct, unchanged onFebruary and compared with 7.2 pct in March 1986.    Istat said its consumer price index for the families ofworkers and employees, base year 1985 equals 100, registered109.5 in March 1987 compared with 109.1 in February this yearand 105.1 in March 1986. REUTER&#3;